text: Klender Baru station is a commuter rail station that is part of the KAI Commuter Jabodetabek system, and is located in Penggillingan, Cakung, East Jakarta, and is part of the rail system's "Zone 1". ==Trains and services== The lines below are the lines that stop and serve in the Klender Baru station. *Blue Line: to Jakarta Kota and Bekasi Category:Railway stations in Jakarta
title: Klender Baru railway station
